snippet: First-year college quarterbacks typically hesitate with both their throws and their words, but Jameis Winston, who leads fifth-ranked Florida State, is not an ordinary freshman.
abstract: First-year college quarterbacks typically hesitate with both their throws and their words, but Jameis Winston, who leads fifth-ranked Florida State, is not an ordinary freshman; he has a veteran’s follow-through with his passes and a senior’s quick with responses that show an ability to keep his cool.
lead_paragraph: First-year college quarterbacks typically hesitate with both their throws and their words, but Jameis Winston, who leads fifth-ranked Florida State, is not an ordinary freshman.

headline.main: At 19, Jameis Winston is a Quick Learner and a Decisive Leader
headline.print_headline: At Florida State, a Quick Learner and a Decisive Leader
